| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2445 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d8831682-8f48-5a5d-ac15-9bc404ebdffb"
